[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering whether the generated test scaffold includes the build argument for GraalVM Native Image, specifically `--enable-url-protocols=jrt`. This is not part of the environment property but is crucial for the setup of certain libraries like Janino, which reads JDK classes through jrt URLs. I’m questioning if meaningful coverage can be achieved without it. The existing tests show that this build argument is included. I need to determine if it's essential for full coverage in this context.
